{"id":54849,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/03/挥刀者说/","date":"2010-03-30T04:02:43Z","modified":"2010-03-30T04:02:43Z","title":"挥刀者说","content":"<p>昨晚烧菜，削茄子皮时偶一失手，拿刀把左手食指削了。<br />\n我下厨多年，时刻牢记安全第一，此系首度自残。</p>\n<p>没什么大事，只削掉皮肉少许。<br />\n止了血，喷了一口某山西老酒，算消了毒。</p>\n<p>只是至今还缠着棉纱，于打字有碍。<br />\n因此，时才所敲这些话……</p>\n<p>——皆未含r、t、f、g、v、b诸字母。</p>\n<p>（最后这一句里的字母由右手食指代劳……）</p>\n<p><img border=\"0\" height=\"0\" src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/347535767/dongdongqiang/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://thisisdongdongqiang.com/archives/1970\" width=\"0\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/dongdongqiang/347535767/art01.html\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/dongdongqiang/347535767/art01.gif\"></a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[8731]}